com.github.dandelion.core.storage

Class StorageEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dandelion.core.storage.StorageEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class StorageEntry
extends Object
implements Serializable

    Wrapper for entries stored in the BundleStorage.

    Mainly used to store the asset contents but also allow to keep track of its metadata once stored in the BundleStorage.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Thibault Duchateau
